The methodology used to calculate the proposed DRG 
relative weights from the FY 1993 MedPAR file is as follows: 
 To the extent possible, all the claims were regrouped 
using the proposed DRG classification revisions discussed 
above in section II.B of this preamble. As noted in section 
II.B.4, due to the unavailability of revised GROUPER 
software, we simulate most major classification changes to 
approximate the placement of cases under the proposed 
