required by section 1886(d)(5)(A)(v) of the Act and discussed above would be: 

 Day outliers_The geometric mean length of stay for each DRG plus the lesser of 21 days or 3 standard deviations.


 Cost outliers_The greater of 2.0 times the prospective payment rate for the DRG or $31,000. 

