beyond the facility's control distort its cost increase for a cost reporting period.
Although the Congress legislates the update to the TEFRA target amounts, ProPAC and the Secretary of Health and Human
Services are required to recommend an annual update factor. For fiscal years 1994 through 1997, each facility will
receive an update ranging from the projected increase in the market basket to the market basket increase minus 1.0
percentage points. The Commission recommends an average update to the target rate equal to the market basket increase
